{ (Some) Menus

   → design/graphic/GIMP/GUI/Menu/Filters/Script-Fu/Console[Filters -> Script Fu -> Console] opens the → design/graphic/GIMP/Fu/Script#script-fu-console

   Directory for → design/graphic/GIMP/Fu/Script scripts: Edit -> Preferences -> Folders -> Scripts

